Description:
            This project aims to reproduce key figures, statistics, tables, and results from the research paper titled:
            "Characterizing Political Fake News in Twitter by its Meta-Data". 
            This was done via R and RMarkdown in RStudio. 
            This compendium hosts all relevant data, code, and replication outputs. 
